reviewText: Awesome very good dvd love it
Anyone who is really into bodybuilding and a true fan of the sport, will enjoy this dvd.  You will get an inside look into how the top bodybuilders in the world train.
Love these videos!  Makes me want to stop watching and go workout!
If you want a DVD to motivate you to get up and work out, here it is! Awesome, to the point, and everything you wanted to know about bodybuilding and training!
